<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>YouTube Video Player</title>
    <style>
        body {
            background-color: #1C2833;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            height: 100vh;
            margin: 0;
        }

        .description-container {
            background-color: #5665734a;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0.1px 8px 8px 2px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .nav-link {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: #3498db;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .error-message {
            color: red;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="description-container">
        <h2>Welcome to YouTube Video Player</h2>
        <p>Experience the world of YouTube videos like never before. Our YouTube Video Player allows you to enjoy your favorite videos directly on our platform. No need to download or install anything.</p>
        <p>Simply enter the YouTube video URL, and watch it with ease. Whether it's music, tutorials, vlogs, or entertainment, our player has you covered. It's fast, convenient, and free to use.</p>
        <p>Discover, watch, and enjoy YouTube content hassle-free. Start exploring now!</p>
        <p id="error-message" class="error-message"></p>
        <a class="nav-link" href="/signup">Sign up for an account</a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
